  "instructions": [
    "heat 1 tablespoon of coconut oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "add the sliced red onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "add the ground cumin, garam masala, and red chili pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the chuck roast and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the dal and water to the wok and bring to a boil.",
    "reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 1 hour.",
    "season the dal with salt to taste.",
    "serve the malaysian chuck roast dal hot, garnished with fresh cilantro."
